OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FAberdeen Chamber of Commerce, perhaps
OL,8,Funsurprisingly, is campaigning
OL,9,Fvigorously on the issue.
OL,11,FAnd STV's senior management faced
OL,12,Fhostile questioning at a Scottish
OL,13,Fparliament committee.
OL,15,FIronically it seems to be the two
OL,16,Fbroadcasting unions which are taking a
OL,17,Fslightly more nuanced approach.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
