OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FThe NUJ and BECTU are both strongly
OL,8,Fopposed to the proposals and fighting
OL,9,Ffor their members' jobs. If compulsory
OL,10,Fredundancies start to look likely, this
OL,11,Fcould become an industrial dispute. The
OL,12,Fproposed editorial changes have been
OL,13,Fbranded cultural vandalism by them.
OL,15,FBut they also recognise the challenges
OL,16,Ffacing the TV industry.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
