OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FTheir concern seems to be that the
OL,8,Fcompany is simply intent on making
OL,9,Fmassive cuts, perhaps in direct
OL,10,Fresponse to its immediate financial
OL,11,Fproblems and share price, rather than
OL,12,Fan insistence that the current format
OL,13,Fof the STV News remains fixed in stone.
OL,15,FIf it were not for the immediacy of the
OL,16,Fsituation, that would be an important
OL,17,Fissue to consider carefully.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
