OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FThere is no doubt that Grampian's
OL,8,Flegacy endures around the north east of
OL,9,FScotland.
OL,11,FThat explains the passion of opponents.
OL,12,FIt is also a credit to the current
OL,13,Fstaff and their predecessors.
OL,15,FBut what sort of news service should be
OL,16,Fprovided by STV?
OL,18,FShould it provide a national service
OL,19,Flike BBC Scotland?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
