OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FShould it provide regional news
OL,8,Fprogrammes for distinct parts of
OL,9,FScotland with some Scottish national
OL,10,Fnews included too?
OL,12,FThe actual boundary between STV's two
OL,13,Fareas reflects the transmitter coverage
OL,14,Fareas.
OL,16,FDo viewers in the Western Isles want a
OL,17,Flocal story from Stonehaven?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
