OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FDo viewers in Perth - practically in
OL,8,Fthe Edinburgh commuter zone - want to
OL,9,Fhear about Shetland?
OL,11,FIt's not a straightforward question.
OL,12,FThis is an issue that needs proper
OL,13,Fexamination.
OL,15,FI'm almost beginning to feel sorry for
OL,16,FOfcom. It will be under intense
OL,17,Fpolitical pressure in Scotland over
OL,18,FSTV's proposals.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
