OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FIt will need to decide whether to
OL,8,Faccept or reject the plan. But it will
OL,9,Falso be mindful of financial realities.
OL,11,FIn short, it only has a limited scope
OL,12,Fto impose loss-making legal obligations
OL,13,Fon STV. The value of a Channel 3
OL,14,Flicence is not what it was.
OL,16,FMy guess is a compromise.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
