OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FSome form of sub-opt will stay. Perhaps
OL,8,F10 minutes dedicated to the Central and
OL,9,FNorth areas within the 6pm programme
OL,10,Fand dedicated bulletins at 10.30pm.
OL,12,FThe examples elsewhere appear to
OL,13,Fsuggest that Ofcom would have no issue
OL,14,Fwith production and presentation in
OL,15,FGlasgow.
OL,17,FNobody would pretend that the north of
OL,18,Fscotland will get a better local
OL,19,Fservice as a result. But is it the best
OL,20,Fthat can realistically be afforded?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
