OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FHow might STV (which made a loss and is
OL,8,Fbarely worth 50m) react if Ofcom
OL,9,Fthrows out its plans completely?
OL,11,FHopefully Ofcom's public consultation
OL,12,Fwill allow all these arguments to be
OL,13,Fvoiced and explored.
OL,15,FThe unions seem able to distinguish
OL,16,Fbetween their members' jobs, their
OL,17,Fconcern for good journalism and simply
OL,18,Fholding on to keeping things the way
OL,19,Fthey were for the sake of doing so.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
