OL,3,GOPINIONCIs compromise Glasgow-based
OL,4,Cproduction/presentation solution best
OL,5,Coutcome for former Grampian region?
OL,6,
OL,7,FIt is important to have an informed
OL,8,Fdebate where the choice is not simply
OL,9,Fbetween the end of Grampian and no
OL,10,Fchange at all.
OL,12,FCan politicians and others whose
OL,13,Fconcern is primarily for the good of
OL,14,Fthe north of Scotland - but who may
OL,15,Fknow little of the realities of
OL,16,Fcommercial television - rise to the
OL,17,Fchallenge of that debate?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
